A Magistrates’ Court in Life Camp, Abuja, on Monday, sentenced a welder, Tasiu Adamu, to six months imprisonment for stealing four cell phones worth N30,000. Magistrate Chinyere Nwecheonwu, sentenced Adamu, who resides in Jabi village, Abuja, after he pleaded guilty to theft. Nwecheonwu, however, gave the convict an option to pay a fine of N12,000. She ordered that the phones recovered from the convict be returned to the complainants. ALSO READ: Garlic, salt water will not protect against coronavirus ― WHO NGOs lament poor budget line for adolescent health services Court slams 10 years jail term on rapist in Kogi BREAKING: Obaseki petitions IGP over Edo APC crisis Brain drain, hindrance to health sector development ― Expert The convict who was given the opportunity to address the court before sentencing begged the court to temper justice with mercy. Earlier, the Prosecution Counsel, Peter Ejike, told the court that Jamilu Usman, a vigilante leader of Dape village, Abuja, reported the matter at the Life Camp Police Station on January 29. Ejike said that the convict broke into shops belonging to Joy Nweke, Adamu Sharo, Faith Gabriel and Ugwu Chidiebere, all of Dape village and stole their phone worth N30,000. The prosecutor, in addition, said that during police investigation, the phones were recovered from the convict. The offence, he said, contravened the provisions of Section 288 of the Penal Code. (NAN) SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!! STAY STRONGER, LONGER AND SATISFY MADAM LIKE NEVER BEFORE WITH THIS NATURAL SUPPLEMENTS WITH NO SIDE EFFECTS. CLICK NOW. CLICK HERE NOW TO WORK FROM HOME ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN CONVINIENCE AND GET PAID WEEKLY, DIRECTLY INTO YOUR SPECIFIED BANK ACCOUNT.REGISTRATION IS ABSOLUTELY FREE. PREMATURE EJACULATION, SMALL SIZE FINALLY CURED NATURALLY IN 2 WEEKS FOR BIGGER, LONGER, HARDER SEXIER SEX WITH NEW MAN MACHINE